{
  "texts": [
    "We used the llama-recipes foot_10 repository, with the AnyPrecisionAdamW optimizer, an initial learning rate of 1e-4 paired with a CosineAnnealingWarmRestarts learning rate scheduler with T_0 set to 0.2 * the length of the training data and T_mult set to 2.",
    "We use LoRA r 16, α 32 and experiment with training for 3 or 4 epochs with a batch size of 4.",
    "For all training performed in this work, we used 8 x A100 GPUs with PyTorch FSDP enabled, with a batch size of 4 and \"packing\" enabled.",
    "The training time is about 15 minutes per epoch on this setup.",
    "In this section, we elaborate the modeling and design choices we made based on experiments on different model settings shown in Table 7."
  ]
}